Result.Name: monthSinceData
Result.Formula: DateDiff(CurrentScopeStart(), Step Monthly) * -1 + 1

Result.Name: YearsFromNow
Result.Formula: DateDiff(CurrentScopeStart(), Step Yearly) * -1 + 0.5

Result.Name: YearsCalendar
Result.Formula: Year() - Year(CurrentScopeStart()) + 1

Result.Name: YearDiff
Result.Formula: MovingDiff(Column "YearsCalendar" in " ",1)

Result.Name: Oil Price RON dynamic
Result.Formula:
If column "YearsCalendar" in " " = 1  Then	ValueFromParent("Oil price (this year)" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy") 
         Elseif column "YearsCalendar" in " " = 2 Then ValueFromParent("Oil price (next year)" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy") 
         Else ValueFromParent("Oil price (two years)" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy") 
         End If

Result.Name: Gas Price RON dynamic
Result.Formula:
If column "YearsCalendar" in " " = 1  Then	ValueFromParent("Gas price (this year)" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy") 
         Elseif column "YearsCalendar" in " " = 2 Then ValueFromParent("Gas price (next year)" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy") 
         Else ValueFromParent("Gas price (two years)" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy") 
         End If

Result.Name: Gas price limit suppl revenue RON dynamic
Result.Formula:
If column "YearsCalendar" in " " = 1  Then	ValueFromParent("gas price limit suppl revenue (this year)" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy") 
         Elseif column "YearsCalendar" in " " = 2 Then ValueFromParent("gas price limit suppl revenue (next year)" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy") 
         Else ValueFromParent("gas price limit suppl revenue (two years)" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy") 
         End If

Result.Name: UOP Values dynamic
Result.Formula:
If column "YearsCalendar" in " " = 1  Then	ValueFromParent("UOP Values (this year)" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy") 
         Else ValueFromParent("UOP Values (next year)" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy") 
         End If

Result.Name: Oil Workover Gain daily
Result.Formula: "Forecast oil rate with WO risked" in "m3/d"  !-  "Forecast oil rate without WO" in "m3/d"

Result.Name: Oil Workover Gain monthly ton
Result.Formula:
If IsEntityType("Section") Then
	     		Column "Oil Workover Gain daily" in "m3/d" * DaysInMonth() * ValueFromParent("oil density static" in "kg/m3","Well","Virtual Well Hierarchy") / 1000 
	    Else Column "Oil Workover Gain daily" in "m3/d" * DaysInMonth() * "oil density static" in "kg/m3" / 1000 
	    End IF

Result.Name: Gas Workover Gain monthly
Result.Formula: ("Forecast gas rate with WO risked" in "m3/d"  !-  "Forecast gas rate without WO" in "m3/d") * DaysInMonth()

Result.Name: Oil Revenue 2
Result.Formula: Column "Oil Workover Gain monthly ton" in "t"  *  Column "Oil Price RON dynamic" in " "

Result.Name: Oil Revenue
Result.Formula: Column "Oil Workover Gain monthly ton" in "t"  * Column "Oil Price RON dynamic" in " "

Result.Name: Gas Revenue
Result.Formula: Column "Gas Workover Gain monthly" in "m3" / 1000 * Column "Gas Price RON dynamic" in " "

Result.Name: Gas tax monthly
Result.Formula:
If (Last(Column "Gas Price RON dynamic" in " ") > ValueFromParent("Price Gas supp limit RON" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy") ) Then
    		Column "Gas Workover Gain monthly" in "m3" / 1000 * (Column "Gas price limit suppl revenue RON dynamic" in " " - ValueFromParent("Price Gas supp limit RON" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy"))*
    		(1-0.3- ValueFromParent("Royalty Gas" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy"))*0.6
    	Else Null() End If

Result.Name: Gas tax final
Result.Formula: If Column "Gas tax monthly" in "RON" < 0.0 Then 0.0 Else Column "Gas tax monthly" in "RON" End If

Result.Name: Oil Royalty monthly
Result.Formula: Column "Oil Revenue" in "RON"  * ValueFromParent("Royalty Oil" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy")

Result.Name: Gas Royalty monthly
Result.Formula: Column "Gas Workover Gain monthly" in "m3" / 1000 * Column "Gas price limit suppl revenue RON dynamic" in " " * ValueFromParent("Royalty Gas" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy")

Result.Name: OPEX Oil
Result.Formula: Column "Oil Workover Gain monthly ton" in "t" * ValueFromParent("OPEX Oil (cost per ton)" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy")

Result.Name: OPEX Gas
Result.Formula: Column "Gas Workover Gain monthly" in "m3" * ValueFromParent("OPEX Gas (cost per 1000m3)" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy") / 1000

Result.Name: OPEX var (oil+gas)
Result.Formula: Column "OPEX Oil" in "RON" !+  Column "OPEX Gas" in "RON"

Result.Name: Revenue Total monthly
Result.Formula: Column "Oil Revenue" in "RON" !+  Column "Gas Revenue" in "RON"

Result.Name: Revenue Risked monthly
Result.Formula: Column "Revenue Total monthly" in "RON" * ValueFromParent("WO Success Rate" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy")

Result.Name: Revenue Net Risked monthly
Result.Formula: Column "Revenue Risked monthly" in "RON" !- Column "Oil Royalty monthly" in "RON" !- Column "Gas Royalty monthly" in "RON" !- Column "Gas tax final" in "RON" !- Column "OPEX Oil" in "RON" !- Column "OPEX Gas" in "RON"

Result.Name: CAPEX deduct
Result.Formula: If (Column "monthSinceData" in " " = 1) Then Input Column "Total cost" in "RON" Else Null() End If

Result.Name: Depreciation
Result.Formula: Input Column "Total cost" in "RON" * Average(Column "UOP Values dynamic" in " ")/12

Result.Name: Infrastructure tax monthly
Result.Formula: Input Column "Total cost" in "RON" * ValueFromParent("infrastructure tax" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy")/12

Result.Name: EBITD monthly
Result.Formula:
If (Column "Revenue Net Risked monthly" in "RON"  > 0.0) Then
	    		Column "Revenue Net Risked monthly" in "RON" 
	    		!- Column "Infrastructure tax monthly" in "RON"
	    	Else Null() End If

Result.Name: EBIT monthly
Result.Formula:
If IsNull(Column "EBITD monthly" in "RON") Then Null()
    	Else Column "EBITD monthly" in "RON" !- Column "Depreciation" in "RON" End If

Result.Name: EBIT annual cum
Result.Formula: MovingSum(Column "EBIT monthly" in "RON",11,0)

Result.Name: Income tax per year
Result.Formula:
If (Column "YearDiff" in " " = 1.0 And Column "EBIT annual cum" in "RON" > 0.0)  Then Round(Column "EBIT annual cum" in "RON" * ValueFromParent("income tax per year" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy") ) 
         Else Null() End If

Result.Name: NPV monthly
Result.Formula:
If (Column "Revenue Net Risked monthly" in "RON"  > 0.0) Then 
    		Column "EBITD monthly" in "RON" !- Column "Income tax per year" in "RON" !- Column "CAPEX deduct" in "RON"
    	Else Null() End If

Result.Name: NPV monthly 9
Result.Formula: Column "NPV monthly" in "RON" / Pow((1.1),Column "YearsFromNow" in " ")

Result.Name: NPV monthly 9 cum
Result.Formula: Cum(Column "NPV monthly 9" in "RON")

Result.Name: NPV monthly 12
Result.Formula: Column "NPV monthly" in "RON" / Pow((1.15),Column "YearsFromNow" in " ")

Result.Name: NPV monthly 12 cum
Result.Formula: Cum(Column "NPV monthly 12" in "RON")

Result.Name: Revenue2
Result.Formula: Round(Sum( Column "Revenue Total monthly" in "RON"))

Result.Name: Subsurface cost manual
Result.Formula: "subsurface cost (manual)"  in "RON"

Result.Name: Subsurface cost
Result.Formula: If  "subsurface cost (manual)" in "RON" > 0.0 Then "subsurface cost (manual)" in "RON" Else "subsurface cost (calculated)" in "RON" End If

Result.Name: Surface cost
Result.Formula: "surface cost (manual)"  in "RON"

Result.Name: Additional cost
Result.Formula: "additional cost (manual)"  in "RON"

Result.Name: Total cost
Result.Formula: Column "Subsurface cost" in "RON" !+ "surface cost (manual)" in "RON"  !+ "additional cost (manual)" in "RON"

Result.Name: Risk factor
Result.Formula:
If Column "Revenue" in "RON" > 0.0 Then
        - Round(Sum(Input Column "Revenue Total monthly" in "RON" !- Input Column "Revenue Risked monthly" in "RON"))     
      Else NULL() End If

Result.Name: Revenue Risked
Result.Formula:
If Column "Revenue" in "RON" > 0.0 
      Then Round(Sum(Input Column "Revenue Risked monthly" in "RON")) Else NULL() End If

Result.Name: Royalties
Result.Formula:
If Column "Revenue" in "RON" > 0.0 Then - Round(Sum(Input Column "Oil Royalty monthly" in "RON" !+ Input Column "Gas Royalty monthly"  in "RON"))
      Else NULL() End If

Result.Name: Gas tax
Result.Formula:
If Column "Revenue" in "RON" > 0.0 Then - Round(Sum(Input Column "Gas tax final" in "RON"))
      Else NULL()End If

Result.Name: OPEX var
Result.Formula:
If Column "Revenue" in "RON" > 0.0 Then -Round(Sum(Input Column "OPEX var (oil+gas)" in "RON"))
      Else NULL() End If

Result.Name: Revenue Net Risked
Result.Formula:
If Column "Revenue" in "RON" > 0.0 Then Round(Sum(Input Column "Revenue Net Risked monthly" in "RON"))
	  Else NULL() End If

Result.Name: Infrastructure Tax
Result.Formula:
If (Column "Revenue" in "RON" > 0) Then - Round(Sum(Input Column "Infrastructure tax monthly" in "RON"))
		Else Null() End If

Result.Name: EBITD
Result.Formula:
If Column "Revenue" in "RON" > 0.0 Then Round(Sum(Input Column "EBITD monthly" in "RON"))
       Else NULL() End If

Result.Name: CAPEX
Result.Formula:
If (Column "Revenue" in "RON" > 0) Then -Round(First(Input Column "CAPEX deduct" in "RON"))
		 Else Null() End If

Result.Name: Income tax
Result.Formula:
If Column "Revenue" in "RON" > 0.0 Then -Round(Sum(Input Column "Income tax per year" in "RON"))
	    Else NULL() End If

Result.Name: NPV risked
Result.Formula:
If "knock out criteria exist" in " " = 1.0 OR Column "Revenue" in "RON" <= 0.0 Then Null() Else
		Round(Sum(Input Column "NPV monthly" in "RON")) End If

Result.Name: Discount 9
Result.Formula:
If Column "Revenue" in "RON" > 0.0 Then Column "NPV 9" in "RON" - Column "NPV risked" in "RON" 
	   Else NULL() End If

Result.Name: NPV 9
Result.Formula:
If "knock out criteria exist" in " " = 1.0 OR Column "Revenue" in "RON" <= 0.0 Then Null() 
		Else Round(Sum(Input Column "NPV monthly 9" in "RON")) End If

Result.Name: Discount
Result.Formula:
If Column "Revenue" in "RON" > 0.0 Then Column "NPV 12" in "RON" - Column "NPV 9" in "RON"
		Else NULL() End If

Result.Name: NPV 12
Result.Formula:
If "knock out criteria exist" in " " = 1.0 OR Column "Revenue" in "RON" <= 0.0 Then Null() Else
		Round(Sum(Input Column "NPV monthly 12" in "RON")) End If

Result.Name: Oil Production
Result.Formula: Round(Sum(Input Column "Oil Workover Gain monthly ton" in "t" ))

Result.Name: Gas Production [1000 m3]
Result.Formula: Round(Sum(Input Column "Gas Workover Gain monthly" in "m3") / 1000)

Result.Name: Oil Price per ton
Result.Formula: Last(Input Column "Oil Price RON dynamic" in " ")

Result.Name: Gas Price per 1000 m3
Result.Formula: Last(Input Column "Gas Price RON dynamic" in " ")

Result.Name: Oil Revenue Sum
Result.Formula: Round(Sum(Input Column "Oil Revenue" in "RON"))

Result.Name: Gas Revenue Sum
Result.Formula: Round(Sum(Input Column "Gas Revenue" in "RON"))

Result.Name: Revenue from Production Gain
Result.Formula: Round(Sum(Input Column "Revenue Total monthly" in "RON"))

Result.Name: Risked Revenue
Result.Formula:
If Input Column "Revenue2" in "RON" > 0.0 Then Round(Sum(Input Column "Revenue Risked monthly" in "RON"))
		Else NULL() End If

Result.Name: Revenue Net (Risked)
Result.Formula:
If Input Column "Revenue2" in "RON" > 0.0 Then Round(Sum(Input Column "Revenue Net Risked monthly" in "RON"))
		Else NULL() End If

Result.Name: Oil Royalty
Result.Formula:
If Input Column "Revenue2" in "RON" > 0.0 Then Last(ValueFromParent("Royalty Oil" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy")) * 100
		Else NULL() End If

Result.Formula:
If Input Column "Revenue2" in "RON" > 0.0 Then Last(ValueFromParent("Royalty Gas" in " ","asset","Virtual Well Hierarchy")) * 100
		Else NULL() End If

Result.Formula:
If Input Column "Revenue2" in "RON" > 0.0 Then Round(Sum(Input Column "Oil Royalty monthly" in "RON"))

Result.Name: CAPEX Total

Result.Name: OPEX (variable)
Result.Formula:
If Input Column "Revenue2" in "RON" > 0.0 Then Round(Sum(Input Column "OPEX var (oil+gas)" in "RON"))
	    Else NULL() End If

Result.Name: Depreciation Sum
Result.Formula:
If Input Column "Revenue2" in "RON" > 0.0 Then Round(Sum(Input Column "Depreciation" in "RON"))

Result.Name: Infrastructure Tax Sum

If Input Column "Revenue2" in "RON" > 0.0 Then Round(Sum(Input Column "Infrastructure tax monthly" in "RON"))

Result.Name: Income Tax Sum
